skills.title: Adrenaline
skills.description: Increases your Skill Cooldown Rate. The fuller your Shield the greater this bonus.

skills.title: Hearty Stock
skills.description: Increases your Maximum Shield.

skills.title: Ready for Action
skills.description: Improves your Shield Recharge Rate and Delay.

skills.title: Brain Freeze
skills.description: Scoring a Critical Hit has a chance to Slow the target. This stacks until the target is Frozen*.

skills.title: Stiff Upper Lip
skills.description: Taking damage, causes you to develop Resistance to that damage type.

skills.title: Rise to the Occasion
skills.description: You gain passive Health Regeneration. The lower your shield the greater this bonus.

skills.title: Distributed Denial
skills.description: Barrier gains the effects of your currently equipped Shield. Your Barrier also shares these shield effects with nearby allies. You receive reduced effects.

skills.title: Really Expensive Jacket
skills.description: Reduces the Duration of Elemental Status Effects applied to you.

skills.title: Best Served Cold
skills.description: Killing an enemy creates a Nova on you, dealing Cryo Area Skill Damage. Cooldown: 3s

skills.title: Futility Belt
skills.description: Killing an enemy, converts elemental damage you take to Physical Damage for a short time. Passively increases Physical Damage Resistance. Physical Resistance: +18% Duration: 8s

skills.title: Refreshment
skills.description: Dealing Damage to Frozen enemies heals you.

skills.title: Calm, Cool, Collected
skills.description: Freezing an enemy starts your Shield Recharge. If your Shield is full, you gain Health Regeneration for a short time. If your Health is full, your Skill Cooldowns or Durations reset. Max-Health Regen/s: 3% Regen Duration: 3s

skills.title: Nerves of Steel
skills.description: While your Shield is full you stack Accuracy and Handling. All stacks are lost upon taking damage. Max Stacks: 15

skills.title: Confident Competence
skills.description: While your Shield is active, you gain increased Gun Damage and Accuracy. The fuller your Shield the great this bonus. Gun Damage: up to +35% Accuracy: up to +50%

skills.title: Synchronicity
skills.description: Each active Action Skill increases your Gun Damage.

skills.title: Praemunitus
skills.description: Increases your and Clone's Magazine Size.

skills.title: Borrowed Time
skills.description: Each active Action Skill* increases Action Skill Duration.

skills.title: Donnybrook
skills.description: Killing an enemy stacks your and Clone's Health Regeneration and Gun Damage for a short time. Clone kills also trigger this skill. Max Stacks: 2 Stack Duration: 8s

skills.title: Fractal Frags
skills.description: Killing an enemy gives Clone a chance to throw a copy of your equipped grenade. On Digi-Clone start and end, Clone always throws a grenade. Chance: 30%

skills.title: Duct Tape Mod
skills.description: You become Immune to your own damage dealt. Your 1st shot after a reload has a chance to throw your equipped grenade. Free grenades if your reserve is empty. This skill has a short cooldown. Cooldown: 8s

skills.title: Quick Breather
skills.description: Swapping places with Clone heals Clone for 50% Missing-Health and starts your Shield Recharge.

skills.title: Pocket Full of Grenades
skills.description: Killing an enemy grants stacking Grenade Regeneration for a short time. Max Stacks: 2 Stack Duration: 8s

skills.title: Old-U
skills.description: You can now press [action-skill] to sacrifice Clone to gain gain a full health Second Wind. Max-Health Restored: 100%

skills.title: Supersonic Man
skills.description: Each active Action Skill* increases your Movement Speed.

skills.title: Like a Ghost
skills.description: You and Clone gain a chance to Evade Bullets. Activating an Action Skill stacks extra Evasion Chance for a short time. Max Stacks: 2 Stack Duration: 8s

skills.title: Boom. Enhance.
skills.description: Activating Digi-Clone consumes up to 3 grenades and increases Clone's Fire Rate, Gun Damage, Reload Speed, Max-Health, and Duration. Fire Rate: +5% /grenade Gun Damage: +20% /grenade Reload Speed: +45% /grenade Max-Health: +81% /grenade Duration: +25% /grenade

skills.title: Trick of the Light
skills.description: You deal Bonus Cryo Damage to enemies who aren't targeting you. SNTNL always deals Bonus Cryo Damage.

skills.title: Double Barrel
skills.description: Activating Digi-Clone now also clones your held Gun, but with less damage. Swapping places with Clone increases your and Clone's Gun Damage. Gun Damage: +25% Clone: Gun Damage: -30%

skills.title: Man of Focus
skills.description: Activating an Action Skill grants you stacking Accuracy and Handling for a short time. Max Stacks: 10 Stack Duration: 12s

skills.title: Renegade
skills.description: Scoring a Critical Hit, grants you Health Regeneration for a short time. Duration: 12s

skills.title: Déjà Vu
skills.description: Killing an enemy with a Critical Hit has a chance to instantly reload 1 ammo*.

skills.title: Headsman's Hand
skills.description: Killing an enemy grants stacking Critical Damage for a short time. Max Stacks: 2 Stack Duration: 8s

skills.title: Tunnel Vision
skills.description: While moving, you gain increased Accuracy and Handling. The faster you move, the greater this bonus.

skills.title: Commitment
skills.description: Killing an enemy grants stacking Gun Damage and Skill Cooldown Rate for a short time. Max Stacks: 2 Stack Duration: 8s

skills.title: Fugitive
skills.description: You can now sprint and shoot at the same time.

skills.title: Domino Effect
skills.description: Scoring a Critical Hit, increases your Fire Rate, Reload Speed and Burst-Fire Delay for a short time. Scoring a Action Skill Critical hit doubles this bonus. Duration: 8s

skills.title: The Art of War
skills.description: Activating an Action Skill or an Action Skill Ability stacks up Gun Damage. Your next shot consumes all stacks. Max Stacks: 10

skills.title: Sheer Will
skills.description: Increases your Skill Cooldown Rate. Scoring a Critical Hit stacks extra Cooldown Rate*. Max Stacks: 15 Stack Duration: 8s

skills.title: Eraser
skills.description: Your and Clone's Critical Hits Pierce enemies once, dealing increasing Damage*.

skills.title: Our Man Flynt
skills.description: Aiming adds Bonus Damage to your guns and scoring a critical hit applies their Status Effect. Bonus Damage: +25%

actionSkills.name: Barrier
actionSkills.description: Zane throws up a shield that can block enemy projectiles. Zane and his allies can shoot through the barrier, dealing increased Gun Damage. Pressing [action-skill] or [grenade] while Barrier is active picks up and holds the Barrier, but the size and bonuses are decreased. Pressing [action-skill] or [grenade] again places the Barrier. Duration: 9s Cooldown: 24s

actionSkills.name: Digi-Clone
actionSkills.description: Zane deploys a holographic decoy of himself. The Clone stays in place, but distracts and fires at enemies. Pressing [action-skill] or [grenade] while the Clone is active causes Zane and the Clone to swap places. Duration: 15s Cooldown: 28s

actionSkills.name: SNTNL
actionSkills.description: Zane summons a flying drone to send forward and attack enemies with a machine gun. Pressing [action-skill] or [grenade] while SNTNL is active causes it to attack the enemy under Zane's crosshairs. Duration: 24s Cooldown: 60s

actionSkills.name: MNTIS Shoulder Cannon
actionSkills.description: Zane equips a shoulder-mounted cannon that can fire powerful shots. Pressing [action-skill] or [grenade] while MNTIS Shoulder Cannon is active causes Zane to fire a missile from the cannon. Cooldown: 18s
